<div>
  <div class="header">
    <p class="date">{{momentDateFormat currentDate "DD MMM YYYY"}}</p>
  </div>

  <p class="address">
    Financial Aid Office
    <br />
    {{institution.address}}
    <br />
    {{institution.city}},
    {{institution.province}}
    <br />
    {{institution.country}},
    {{institution.postalCode}}
  </p>

  <p class="saluation">
    Attention Financial Aid:
  </p>

  <p>The Government of Yukon's Student Financial Assistance (SFA) office has approved Yukon Grant
    funding for the following student:</p>

  <p>
    <span>
      <span class="inline-block w-[150px]">Name:</span>
      <span>{{student.lastName}}, {{student.firstName}}</span>
    </span>

    <span>
      <span class="inline-block w-[150px]">Student ID:</span>
      <span>{{student.identificationCode}}</span>
    </span>

    <span>
      <span class="inline-block w-[150px]">Study Period:</span>
      <span>{{momentDateFormat studyPeriod.endDate "MMM Do, YYYY"}}
        to
        {{momentDateFormat studyPeriod.endDate "MMM Do,
        YYYY"}}</span>
    </span>

    <span>
      <span class="inline-block w-[150px]">Amount:</span>
      <span>{{momentDateFormat studyPeriod.endDate "MMM Do, YYYY"}}
        to
        {{momentDateFormat studyPeriod.endDate "MMM Do,
        YYYY"}}</span>
    </span>
  </p>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Amount<span class="ml-4"></span></th>
        <th>Issue Date</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each disbursements}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{centsToDollarString this.amountInCents}}</td>
          <td>{{momentDateFormatDefault this.releaseDate "MMM YYYY" "Upon confirmation"}}</td>
        </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>
    The Yukon Grant is intended to assist the above-named student with full-time post-secondary
    education costs. If any of this information is incorrect, or if this student withdraws or drops
    to part-time status, please notify our office immediately.
  </p>

  <p>
    The Yukon Grant is paid directly to the student, and the first payment has been issued. The
    student is required to submit a Program Information Form (PIF) confirming full-time status prior
    to the release of any subsequent disbursements. Our office will accept PIFs as early as one
    month before the issue date(s) outlined above.
  </p>

  <p>
    If you have any questions, please feel free to contact Yukon SFA at
    <a href="tel:867-667-5929">867-667-5929</a>
    or by email at
    <a href="mailto:sfa@yukon.ca">sfa@yukon.ca</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Sincerely,
  </p>
  <p class="mt-10">
    {{studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.firstName}}
    {{studentFinancialAssistanceOfficer.lastName}}
    <br />
    Student Financial Services Officer
    <br />
    Student Funding Programs
  </p>
</div>
